        `${m.totalSoftwareRecords} software inventory row(s) were found across ${m.distinctSoftware} distinct software name(s).`,
        `${m.missingIp + m.missingModel + m.missingMapping} endpoint identity/data-quality issue(s) may affect reporting confidence.`
